<section id="inscribete" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-box reveal">
      <div class="cta-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <p class="eyebrow-light">Lugares limitados</p>
      <h2>Tu yo del futuro ya sabe usar agentes de IA</h2>
      <p class="cta-sub">
        Inscríbete hoy y en pocas semanas estarás construyendo automatizaciones
        que te ahorran horas de trabajo cada día.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-light">Inscríbete ahora</a>
        <a href="#cursos" class="cta-link">Comparar cursos →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-box {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--gradient-main);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 72px 40px;
    text-align: center;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .cta-glow {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgb(250 204 21 / 0.25), transparent 45%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgb(255 255 255 / 0.15), transparent 45%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .eyebrow-light {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent-yellow);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 16px auto 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .cta-sub {
    color: rgb(255 255 255 / 0.85);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 16px auto 0;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .cta-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 32px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .btn-light {
    background: #fff;
    color: var(--accent-blue);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgb(15 23 42 / 0.2);
  }

  .btn-light:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgb(15 23 42 / 0.3);
  }

  .cta-link {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    opacity: 0.9;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
  }

  .cta-link:hover {
    opacity: 1;
  }
</style>
